Name: Cathy's apartment
Description: Jay and Adnan went to Cathy's apartment in the early evening on January 13th. Jay said they were there when a police officer called Adnan looking for Hae.

Name: Best Buy
Description: Jay told the police in his second interview that Adnan showed him Hae's body in the trunk of her car here.

Name: Woodlawn High School
Description: Hae and Adnan were seniors in the magnet program here. Jay had graduated from the regular high school program a year ahead of them.

Name: Westview Shopping Center
Description: Jay told the police that Adnan threw Hae's wallet and car keys, as well as the shovels they used, into dumpsters at this mall.

Name: I-70 Park and Ride
Description: Jay told the police that Adnan left Hae's body in the trunk of her car at this Park and Ride, before going back to school for track practice.

Name: Hae's body
Description: Hae's body was found 127 feet from Franklintown Road.

Name: Hae's car
Description: Jay told the police that Adnan ditched Hae's car in a grassy parking area here after burying her in Leakin Park.

Name: Intersection where Adnan shows Jay Hae's body
Description: Jay told the police in his first interview that Adnan showed him Hae's body in the trunk of her car here.

Name: Forest Park
Description: Jay told the police in his second interview that he and Adnan drove to this neighborhood to buy weed, after leaving Hae's car at the Park and Ride.

Name: Campfield Early Learning Center
Description: Hae was supposed to pick up her cousin here around 3:15 p.m.

Name: Owings Mills Mall
Description: Hae worked at the LensCrafters in this mall. She may have been headed here after school to leave a note for Don.
